<div class="propose-a-pilot-project">

<div class="container">
  <%= title "Propose a pilot project" %>
</div>

<div class="flex">
  <div class="half">
    <div class="container">

      <p>Do you want to use WikiHouse to build your project? </p>

      <p>The first WikiHouse technology is now in Beta, but there is not yet an established supply chain to provide it. </p>

      <p>Over the next two years, we will be developing new web tools and growing a wider network of architects, manufacturers, builders, insurers and suppliers ready to help you realise your project. In the meantime, there are a number of pilots happening around the world, from tiny studios to homes to whole neighbourhoods. If you would like your project to be one of these pilots, please take 5 minutes to tell us about it.</p>

